      },
      "date": "2014-11-20 04:32:10.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/caccee9e-706b-11e4-a6ba-5254006e85c2).  Ran 18 tests.  2 tests failed: conf-sanity, sanity.",
